{"tid":586150,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"困lift強行開門逃生 母子被監生夾死","createTime":"2018-03-09T09:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T11:20:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed506f6e5daef2592a1fb59cd511338fd40a5877","tid":586150,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:30:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180309/20327010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20327010&d=bDcA%2BvpgglXda%2FJiIXtek26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=424ee209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180309%2F20327010&h=a43b028e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180309/20327010</a><br />\n<br />\n困lift強行開門逃生<br />\n母子被監生夾死<br />\n<br />\n國際新聞   <br />\n         <br />\n俄羅斯克里米亞發生升降機殺人事件，一對母子死亡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n娜塔利亞（Natalia Simonova）推着6個月大兒子外出散步，由所住大廈9樓乘搭升降機時，升降機在3至4樓之間突然停下，娜塔利亞強行掰開升降機門，試從夾縫中將嬰兒車推出升降機外，但嬰兒車卻被升降機門夾住，接着升降機突然上上落落，將她的兒子監生夾死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n娜塔利亞致電在家的丈夫奧列格（Oleg），哭着說兒子已死。奧列格與一名親戚趕落事發樓層，與鄰居合力撬開升降機門。他見到兒子連嬰兒車被夾住，兒子呈倒吊狀態。他們鋸斷嬰兒車之際，升降機又突然上升，也將娜塔利亞夾死。母子相隔五分鐘先後被升降機奪命。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n奧列格對妻兒突然離世難以接受，將他們遺體放進同一棺木埋葬。奧列格現時要獨力照顧兩名分別14和8歲的兒女。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當局就事故展開刑事調查。居民指升降機日久失修，當局又沒有好好修理。奧列格表明會控告大廈的管理公司。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》"},{"pid":"648ec28cd5c98765393e6f5bd1292369d8975f08","tid":586150,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:31:59.000Z","msg":"列做自殺算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e142982807b5710838da2b9607658a253437f826","tid":586150,"uid":37458,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"以為強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57bfbe2761fc6e24b0429df9d0716f5c8808724","tid":586150,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"死於on9"},{"pid":"77aec64de378023050dff3b35c26310bedd17d56","tid":586150,"uid":62514,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T09:45:53.000Z","msg":"有無示意圖睇下"},{"pid":"671b33aeea31b7eaa9ea667e3170115281fcff4f","tid":586150,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"克里米亞唔係烏克蘭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c69d5de7d683b954deb5bfc64dc3175199dcede","tid":586150,"uid":46002,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"671b33aeea31b7eaa9ea667e3170115281fcff4f","tid":586150,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"克里米亞唔係烏克蘭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"入左俄好耐啦"},{"pid":"4eff6a1cc5f7345fadec7323ec72ed49152b44b5","tid":586150,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:40:08.000Z","msg":"好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f443fb871569dfe51497a854f579fff5c839ec1","tid":586150,"uid":49697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"死神來了"},{"pid":"9e2d735179e5697ee17eb8403f19b131007d62f0","tid":586150,"uid":30563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"671b33aeea31b7eaa9ea667e3170115281fcff4f","tid":586150,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"克里米亞唔係烏克蘭咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-09T10:41:08.000Z","msg":"衰咩坐咁耐?"},{"pid":"c181acd006321fb460c57013ce706d760520cc10","tid":586150,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":